I knew it was him.

41:05.714 --> 41:08.626
Well, the important things,
we don’t really know why.

41:08.717 --> 41:10.207
I do not agree with that.

41:10.302 --> 41:11.917
How about love?

41:12.012 --> 41:13.752
I know exactly
why I love you.

41:13.847 --> 41:16.213
Really? Okay.
Why don’t you give me
your top three reasons?

41:16.308 --> 41:18.970
Uh, first,
you love me.

41:19.061 --> 41:21.393
Second,
you love Christine.

41:21.480 --> 41:23.971
- Uh-huh.
— Third, you—

41:24.066 --> 41:26.057
— Gets mysterious, right?
— No, let me gather my thoughts.

41:26.151 --> 41:29.188
That’s exactly why
we have music and poetry, Bones.

41:29.279 --> 41:32.066
Third, your physicality
is remarkable.

41:32.157 --> 41:35.240
Now you give me three
of your top reasons
for loving me.

41:35.327 --> 41:37.534
I don’t have reasons.

41:37.621 --> 41:39.111
[ Chuckles ]

41:39.206 --> 41:40.946
What?

41:41.041 --> 41:43.327
I think what you just said
is very romantic.

41:43.418 --> 41:45.249
What can I say?
I’m a romantic, Bones.

41:45.337 --> 41:47.498
Shall we? Huh?
We shall.

41:47.589 --> 41:50.046
Wine and dine, candle time?

41:50.175 --> 41:52.757
[ Chuckling ]
What does that mean?
I have no idea.

41:54.429 --> 41:56.545
[ Saroyan ]
Do you think Hodgins
will keep our secret?

41:56.682 --> 41:58.968
Yes.
From Angela?

41:59.059 --> 42:01.971
No. I’d be surprised
if she didn’t know
right now.

42:02.062 --> 42:04.553
And do you think Angela
can keep from telling Brennan?

42:04.648 --> 42:06.559
No. Not for long.

42:06.650 --> 42:10.609
Oh, man.
You need to learn how to lie.

42:10.696 --> 42:13.529
I’ll tell you what though.
It stops with Brennan.

42:13.657 --> 42:16.444
You don’t think
she’ll tell Booth?
No, only if he asks.

42:16.535 --> 42:17.741
Oh, God.

42:17.828 --> 42:20.991
And what are the chances
he asks that question?

42:21.081 --> 42:23.197
I’m sorry.

42:23.291 --> 42:25.452
I know you want
to keep this a secret.

42:25.544 --> 42:29.253
Oh, Arastoo, I don’t want
to keep this a secret at all.

42:32.467 --> 42:34.173
Except from
all the other interns.

42:34.261 --> 42:35.626
Definitely.

42:35.762 --> 42:39.129
And everyone who works
at the Jeffersonian.
Damn straight.

42:41.685 --> 42:43.892
You want me to quit?

42:43.979 --> 42:47.312
And live with that guilt?
Oh, no, thanks.

42:49.025 --> 42:50.981
Soto sum it up,

42:51.069 --> 42:54.937
you want to tell everyone,
but you don’t want
anyone to know.

42:55.031 --> 42:57.522
[ Sighs ]
Crazy, right?

42:58.535 --> 43:00.025
No, it’s poetic.

43:53.632 --> 43:55.042
What’s that mean?
